    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 15th level, when you cast a Bukijutsu that uses a Katana or Odachi that has multiple attacks, you may choose to instead make one attack and deal the damage from all attacks. If you were to score a Critical Hit while using this feature, you do not double all damage dice, only the damage dice of what would have been the first attack</p>",
